						               													<description>&amp;raquo;Hot Six&amp;laquo;&amp;nbsp;&amp;hellip;&amp;nbsp;is a trick-taking game, where you try to guess your tricks. This might seem traditional, but the deck is quite innovative: All the suits are made up of a different amount of cards. Additionally, you might want to avoid the &amp;raquo;hot SIX&amp;laquo;.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Deal all the cards and reveal a new trump-suit for this round. Then, a game round consists of 3 phases:&amp;#10;a) Card swapping: Everybody swaps a card with their right and left neighbour.&amp;#10;b) Betting: Count to three. Then everybody indicates with their fingers, how many tricks they want to make this round.&amp;#10;c) Playing: One player leads a trick, the others have to follow suit.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;After the last trick, add up the scores for every player:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;+ 1 point per trick&amp;#10;&amp;#10;+10 points, if you won your bet&amp;#10;-6 points, if you have the &amp;raquo;hot 6&amp;laquo;&amp;#10;When a player has 50 or more points, the game ends and the player with the most points wins.&amp;#10;NOTE: You'll find a 2 player-variant here on BGG.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash; GERMAN &amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Hei&amp;szlig;e 6 &amp;hellip;&amp;nbsp;ist ein Kartenspiel, bei dem man seine Stiche voraussagen m&amp;ouml;chte. Dies wird etwas erschwert durch die Tatsache, dass alle Spielfarben eine unterschiedliche Anzahl an Karten haben. Au&amp;szlig;erdem gilt es die &amp;raquo;hei&amp;szlig;e 6&amp;laquo; zu vermeiden.&amp;#10;Eine 2-Spieler-Variante findet sich hier auf BGG.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash; FRENCH &amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Hot 6 est un jeu de plis, o&amp;ugrave; vous essayez de deviner les plis que vous allez remporter. Cela peut sembler traditionnel, mais le jeu est assez innovant&amp;nbsp;: toutes les couleurs de cartes ont un nombre diff&amp;eacute;rent de cartes. De plus, vous devez essayer d&amp;lsquo;&amp;eacute;viter d&amp;lsquo;avoir le &amp;bdquo;hot 6&amp;ldquo;.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash; DUTCH &amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;ndash;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Hot 6 is een slagenspel waarbij je het aantal slagen dat je gaat halen probeert te voorspellen. Dit lijkt misschien op een traditioneel slagenspel, maar het kaartendeck is innovatief: alle kleuren hebben een verschillend aantal kaarten.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
